content: No results matching your query could be found

comment.text: This translation key is used for the "EmptyFormGalleryScreenDescription" text, which appears on an empty form gallery screen as a message when no results match the user's query. It is likely displayed in a dialog or card component, indicating that no data was found. Translators should provide a concise and descriptive phrase to convey this message in other languages.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation is overly formal and doesn't quite capture the naturalness of the English phrase 'No results matching your query could be found'. While technically correct, it's less user-friendly.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Aucun résultat ne correspond à votre recherche.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'ເຈົ້າ' (jâo) should be 'ທ່ານ' (thān) for more formal and appropriate tone in this context. 'ເຈົ້າ' is more casual and might not be suitable for a formal application interface.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ບໍ່ພົບຜົນການຊອກຫາທີ່ກົງກັບຄຳຊອກຫາຂອງທ່ານ

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation is overly formal and doesn't quite capture the natural tone of the English phrase. 'Interogării dvs' is quite formal for a user-facing message.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Nu am găsit niciun rezultat care să corespundă căutării tale.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While grammatically correct, 'a putut fi găsit' is a bit awkward. A more natural phrasing would be better.

The translation 'ඔබගේ විමසුමට කිසිවක් නොගැළපේ' while understandable, is a somewhat literal translation and doesn't flow as naturally as it could in Sinhala for this context. It translates directly to 'Nothing matches your query'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: A more natural translation could be 'අවශ්‍යතම ප්‍රතිඵලයක් නොදනී' (Avashyathama pratiphalam nanidee) which means 'No results were found' or 'No matching results were found'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation "没有找到匹配查询的结果" is technically correct but sounds slightly formal and unnatural in common usage. A more natural phrasing would be more conversational.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: 没有找到符合您搜索的结果
